                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                        <p>Verified tutors with proven experience</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                        <p>Flexible scheduling that fits your timeline</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                        <p>Direct messaging and virtual classroom integration</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
 
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- How it Works Section -->
<section class="how-it-works">
    <div class="progress-bar">
        <div class="progress-fill"></div>
        <div class="progress-points">
            <div class="point" data-section="0"></div>
            <div class="point" data-section="1"></div>
            <div class="point" data-section="2"></div>
            <div class="point" data-section="3"></div>
            <div class="point" data-section="4"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-container">
        <h1 class="section-title">How Does It Work?</h1>
        
        <div class="how-it-works-section" id="section1">
            <div class="section-content">
                <div class="text-content">
                    <h2>1. Create Your Profile</h2>
                    <p>Tell us about your learning goals, preferred subjects, and schedule. Our smart system uses this information to find your perfect match.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="image-content">
                    <img src="~/images/step1.png" alt="Create Profile" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="how-it-works-section" id="section2">
            <div class="section-content">
                <div class="text-content">
                    <h2>2. Browse Tutors</h2>
                    <p>Explore our verified tutors' profiles, reviews, and ratings. Filter by subject, price, and availability.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="image-content">
                    <img src="~/images/step2.png" alt="Browse Tutors" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="how-it-works-section" id="section3">
            <div class="section-content">
                <div class="text-content">
                    <h2>3. Schedule Sessions</h2>
                    <p>Book sessions directly through our platform. Manage your schedule and communicate with your tutor.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="image-content">
                    <img src="~/images/step3.png" alt="Schedule Sessions" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="how-it-works-section" id="section4">
            <div class="section-content">
                <div class="text-content">
                    <h2>4. Start Learning</h2>
                    <p>Join virtual sessions, track your progress, and achieve your learning goals with personalized support.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="image-content">
                    <img src="~/images/step4.png" alt="Start Learning" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="action-section">
    <div class="action-content">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <h2 class="display-4 mb-4">Get The App Now</h2>
            <div class="action-buttons">
                <a href="#" class="store-button">
                    <img src="~/images/AppStoreBadgeUSUK.svg" alt="Download on App Store">
                </a>
                <a href="#" class="store-button">
                    <img src="~/images/PlayStoreBadgeUSUK.png" alt="Get it on Google Play">
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>